About this Item

This is a great 8 x 10 promotional still from Fiend Without a Face starring Terry Kilburn and Marshall Thompson. This intreging item is perfect for framing or as a gift for those classic film lovers. This still seems to depict a painful moment for this particular character in the film. Wonderful condition. - GRADE: FN. Seller Inventory # U2-113-030
